Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.49,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Snap!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.14,0:00:05.01,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I’ll always be your partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.01,0:00:06.04,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A ferocious alien species!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.04,0:00:09.21,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Something unexpected between the pond’s troublesome\Nnew resident and the man who wishes to raise it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.21,0:00:10.73,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.73,0:00:12.22,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.22,0:00:14.36,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
