Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.29,0:02:09.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}“Beika Central Park — Beika City”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.65,0:02:12.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What’s going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.40,0:02:14.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Detective Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.82,0:02:16.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it’s you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.43,0:02:17.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there another case?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.71,0:02:18.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.86,0:02:20.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At Fukurokoji-{\i1}san{\i0}’s house just over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.41,0:02:23.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Late last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.52,0:02:29.37,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.62,0:02:33.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Just like that, he let the thief get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.06,0:02:36.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He was robbed of about 3 million yen in cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.74,0:02:39.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The culprit wore gloves, giving us nothing\Nto cross-reference as far as fingerprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.96,0:02:45.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He was also wearing a ski mask, so we don’t\Nhave much of an idea as to what he looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.43,0:02:48.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All we know is that he’s a tall, thin male.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.13,0:02:49.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re scouting for witnesses now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.31,0:02:53.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you won’t be needing the Detective Boys’ help, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.21,0:02:55.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, interrogating suspects and searching\Nfor evidence is the job of a police officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.45,0:02:57.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.27,0:02:58.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We still have to go to Central Park, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.70,0:03:01.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of Central Park...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.73,0:03:02.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.98,0:03:05.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This morning, City Hall received news about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:11.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stand back, it’s dangerous here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.84,0:03:13.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please move away from the pond.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:14.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where? Is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.56,0:03:15.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t push me, Genta!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:17.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}’s actually scared, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.83,0:03:18.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.11,0:03:22.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.11,0:03:23.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.09,0:03:25.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.07,0:03:28.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was definitely a snapping turtle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.36,0:03:30.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Snapping turtle?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.97,0:03:41.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did someone raise it as a pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:44.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Or did Japan have this kind of turtle to begin with?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.90,0:03:47.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It may have been abandoned by its owner after\Nthey discovered they could no longer raise it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.48,0:03:49.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s called a snapping turtle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.34,0:03:52.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Its habitat stretches from North America to Mexico.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.17,0:03:55.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s highly aggressive, and the power of its jaws is astonishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:03:57.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Without much effort, they can snap a human finger in half.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:03:59.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a scary creature...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:01.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How could anybody keep it as a pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.88,0:04:05.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are all types of people in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:10.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe raising a pet like that filled a void in their life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:12.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Must be quite a lonely person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.91,0:04:15.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are more and more lonely people like that, aren’t there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.78,0:04:18.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder reptiles are so popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.62,0:04:21.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don’t really care about reptiles, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.00,0:04:23.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We maybe able to understand those that raise them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:27.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Raising a pet can be pretty liberating, but to\Ntoss one away is just being irresponsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.90,0:04:28.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:29.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.89,0:04:35.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention that animals like those are not\Nnative to Japan, and could disrupt our ecosystem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.06,0:04:36.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:38.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s wrong with having more animals around?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.65,0:04:41.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s not the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.39,0:04:43.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But still, we can’t just leave that snapping turtle here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.52,0:04:47.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s find the person who left their frightened turtle here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.97,0:04:48.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.71,0:04:50.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a job for the Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:53.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, where do we start?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.25,0:04:57.20,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The Detective Boys: Defenders of Justice, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:07.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Then, how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.08,0:05:12.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s find the pet shop that the turtle’s owner would usually go to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.01,0:05:13.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Snapping turtles eat a lot, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:18.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They must’ve gone out a lot to buy small fish\Nand prawns to make turtle food, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.95,0:05:20.17,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Figure it out yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:21.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.41,0:05:22.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s get moving, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.73,0:05:23.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re really clever, aren’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.73,0:05:26.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s wrong, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.13,0:05:33.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re the one who abandoned that snapping turtle, aren’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:44.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally found a boyfriend...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:44.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.75,0:05:52.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn’t like reptiles very much, did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:53.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.63,0:05:56.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, things just got complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.68,0:05:58.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t that good though?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:06:01.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To have found someone who can cure your loneliness?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.47,0:06:05.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, no matter how you explain it,\Nabandoning an animal like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.29,0:06:07.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Haibara-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:10.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just remembered that I have something to do, so I’m leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.87,0:06:16.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.14,0:06:17.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It got away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.93,0:06:19.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.16,0:06:21.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s Kamejiro, the turtle that I raised.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.76,0:06:24.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re the owner of that snapping turtle?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.85,0:06:26.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:27.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Nihonmatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.93,0:06:30.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I live in an apartment in the third district.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.75,0:06:34.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, I turned away for a second, and it ran off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.07,0:06:36.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought that it would come all the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.80,0:06:38.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.11,0:06:40.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and give me the snapping turtle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.62,0:06:43.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.87,0:06:45.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The turtle is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.83,0:06:49.61,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A turtle with more than one owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.61,0:06:51.13,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}How interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.73,0:06:53.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.76,0:06:56.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that turtle really yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.09,0:06:58.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no mistaking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.45,0:07:00.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Turtles like these are rarely seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.24,0:07:01.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that’s weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:04.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That lady said that she left it here yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.83,0:07:14.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought that the real owner would show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.49,0:07:16.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you claiming that that turtle is yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:19.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Er, well, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:20.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To atone for my wrongdoings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:21.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Atone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:26.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was little, I bought a green turtle at the local fair to raise as a pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:29.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I got tired of raising it, and it became more and more of a hassle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:32.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I released it into a nearby pond.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.29,0:07:35.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Afterwards, I kept regretting what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.33,0:07:38.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When I heard this morning that a snapping turtle was found at this pond...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.67,0:07:41.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that it had to be one that someone else abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:43.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The turtle never did anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.26,0:07:44.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt sorry for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.21,0:07:48.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I wanted to take it home to raise it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.42,0:07:51.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To make up for abandoning that green turtle long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.11,0:07:53.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So that’s what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.01,0:07:54.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.11,0:07:55.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimata-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:57.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give me that turtle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.59,0:07:59.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll take good care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.34,0:08:00.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:05.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I should be the one begging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.77,0:08:07.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please continue to raise it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.20,0:08:09.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:11.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I will, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:16.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s great, Nihonmatsu-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.00,0:08:20.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For that snapping turtle, it’s probably the best case scenario, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.87,0:08:23.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It really found the best possible owner, right, Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.62,0:08:29.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Could it be—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:32.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.26,0:08:33.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:36.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that’s not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:37.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.71,0:08:45.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are two—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:46.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Snapping turtles!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.12,0:08:47.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s one over here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.38,0:08:49.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s another over here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.42,0:08:54.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With all of them, there’s a total of...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:08:56.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Four...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:59.35,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What’s going on in this pond?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:02.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Nihonmatsu-{\i1}san{\i0}, which turtle is yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.28,0:09:05.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.77,0:09:07.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.12,0:09:10.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give me all of the snapping turtles in the pond.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.69,0:09:12.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A-All of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:17.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, these turtles must’ve been mating. It’d be cruel to separate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.99,0:09:19.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nihonmatsu-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.57,0:09:23.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re such a nice person!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.28,0:09:24.73,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Don’t cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:27.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Say, that finger...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.32,0:09:29.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.64,0:09:31.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:34.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.03,0:09:37.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Got one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:52.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, that’s how they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.44,0:09:54.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly springing up out of the water\Nand biting people, the little punks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:56.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:10:00.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if you look closely, it’s still pretty cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:03.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I still really like turtles, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:06.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be because you raised\Na green turtle a long time ago, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:09.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that’s probably it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:11.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That turtle is cute and beautiful, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:15.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The green on its shell gets brighter as it grows, doesn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.66,0:10:18.98,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}This guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:24.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}You’re talking about that guy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.61,0:10:26.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What don’t you believe about him, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:28.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:31.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this type of green turtle, for example.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.68,0:10:36.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Only when the turtle is in its infancy is its shell a bright green color.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:38.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Over time, it becomes black.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:40.47,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Beautiful, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.47,0:10:43.87,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The green on its shell gets brighter as it grows, doesn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:46.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It just isn’t possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.07,0:10:48.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If he really raised one before, he’d definitely know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.52,0:10:50.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn’t that a lie, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:52.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The part about abandoning the turtle too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.60,0:10:53.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.70,0:10:56.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That so-called admission of guilt was a total fraud.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:10:58.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.00,0:11:00.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That person doesn’t think turtles are cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.67,0:11:02.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,On the contrary, it seems that he doesn’t like them at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:04.32,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That’s how they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.32,0:11:06.39,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Suddenly springing up out of the water\Nand biting people, the little punks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.83,0:11:08.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That whole thing was just a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:12.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did he want to take all\Nfour of the snapping turtles away?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:16.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think he’s bringing them to the Dragon Palace\Nso that the turtles have to repay him for saving them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.23,0:11:17.37,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oh, geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.37,0:11:18.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:23.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever his motive is, I’m going to figure it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.43,0:11:24.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:26.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Genta, keep an eye on that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.55,0:11:27.08,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.55,0:11:27.08,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:29.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of person is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:31.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn’t seem too bad, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.07,0:11:35.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like he has a lot of debt,\Nin addition to all of the rent he owes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:38.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To us, he’s a pretty bothersome tenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.68,0:11:40.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems as if he has money troubles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.87,0:11:45.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And there doesn’t seem to be any unusual\Npurchases of snapping-turtle food.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:49.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So he wants to sell them rather than raise them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.03,0:11:53.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, snapping turtles only cost about\Nseven or eight thousand yen each.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:56.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he sold all four of them, it still\Nwouldn’t be enough to cover his rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.73,0:11:58.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If he doesn’t intend to sell them...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.66,0:12:00.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then there has to be some other reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.15,0:12:04.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Got the second one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:08.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But to raise four turtles...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.34,0:12:09.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What about your sink?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.73,0:12:13.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s true, I should get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.20,0:12:15.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you catch all four of them, let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.56,0:12:16.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I’ll see you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.80,0:12:21.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything’s gone well, so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:24.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But originally, there was only supposed to be one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.62,0:12:26.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And now there are four...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.74,0:12:29.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s sighing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:35.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he really only wanted one of the\Nfour snapping turtles specifically.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.49,0:12:38.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But they got mixed up, and he can’t tell them apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.19,0:12:41.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It’d be better to just take them all back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:44.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The one he wants is among the four, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.68,0:12:49.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be something special about that turtle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.15,0:12:54.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.24,0:12:55.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With interest, the total is 1 million yen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.24,0:12:59.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have the money ready, but something came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:01.30,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}1 million yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.42,0:13:04.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I’ll definitely pay off all of my debts today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:08.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The consequences of eating one’s words...\NYou should be aware of them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.93,0:13:13.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and get that turtle for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.95,0:13:16.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What did he mean by that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.14,0:13:20.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Once he gets that snapping turtle,\Nhe can pay off his debts...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.98,0:13:24.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that turtle have to do with 1 million yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.52,0:13:25.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.09,0:13:31.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because there’s some kind of map on its shell\Nthat leads you to some kind of treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.75,0:13:37.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Genta-{\i1}kun{\i0}, who would have the time to draw a map like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:38.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:43.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Granny, let me give you a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:46.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good timing, Genta-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.49,0:13:48.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Got the third one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.59,0:13:51.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s only one left...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.09,0:13:53.46,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The snapping turtle and 1 million yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.59,0:14:00.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.00,0:14:00.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:05.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Takagi mentioned it earlier this morning, didn’t he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.60,0:14:09.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,About a thief who struck last night,\Nwearing gloves and this kind of mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.65,0:14:11.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m gonna go find Detective Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.19,0:14:11.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.98,0:14:14.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven’t confirmed that this belongs to the burglar yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.24,0:14:17.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But the time matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:19.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was raining a bit last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:20.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet this isn’t wet at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.89,0:14:22.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Which also means...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.24,0:14:25.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was burnt some time after the rain\Nstopped last night and this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:27.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:31.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, this is likely what happened last night, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.86,0:14:36.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The thief escaped to here after stealing\Nthe 3 million yen from that house.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.51,0:14:38.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So the stuff he used last night was also disposed of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:50.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s possible that the two events are somehow related.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.77,0:14:51.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Which two events?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.71,0:14:58.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night’s burglary, and Nihonmatsu-{\i1}san{\i0} wanting\Nto find out the snapping turtle in the pond.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:10.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, doesn’t that mean the man named\NNihonmatsu was actually last night’s burglar?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.09,0:15:14.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn’t you say that the culprit was a tall, skinny male?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.24,0:15:15.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we did say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.51,0:15:18.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s a tall and skinny person, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.40,0:15:19.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And he also said this:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.38,0:15:23.48,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I’ll definitely pay off all of my debts today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:26.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Furthermore, there’s also a bandage around his finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.52,0:15:30.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I’d guess that he hurt his finger when\Nhe was trying to burn the evidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:32.27,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That’s how they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.27,0:15:34.41,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Suddenly springing up out of the water\Nand biting people, the little punks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.41,0:15:38.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Or possibly by being bitten by a snapping turtle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:42.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But there’s one thing I don’t quite understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.87,0:15:47.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, like why he even raised snapping turtles to begin with, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.66,0:15:48.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I already know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:50.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.46,0:15:54.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For whatever reason, after he ran off with\Nthe money and escaped here last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:01.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He took off his ski mask,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:02.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,took off his gloves...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:05.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And he planned on burning the evidence here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:06.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But at that moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.61,0:16:16.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,his finger was bitten by a turtle,\Nwho must’ve seen his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.87,0:16:24.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}But in this pond, there are a total of four turtles.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.95,0:16:29.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Because he couldn’t recognize which turtle\Nit was, he had to get rid of all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:31.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}, if that guy’s the culprit and\Nhe already got the 3 million yen,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.81,0:16:33.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,why can’t he pay off his debt?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:35.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that’s the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:38.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The fourth and last one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:44.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.35,0:16:49.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to find the guy from this morning\Nwho told us about the snapping turtles?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:52.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t think he gave us his name, but he was male.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.97,0:16:54.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And his voice sounded pretty young on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.61,0:17:01.41,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Maybe he thought that he couldn’t catch\Nthem all, so he asked City Hall for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:05.42,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But why would he want the snapping turtles so badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:09.42,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I have the money ready, but something came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:13.41,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What was the “something” that came up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.41,0:17:17.39,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Last night, one of these snapping turtles bit his finger...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.39,0:17:20.01,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But that doesn’t explain everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.50,0:17:21.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Wow, so big!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.80,0:17:23.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Something looks hidden there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.30,0:17:24.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu-{\i1}chan{\i0}, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.45,0:17:24.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:26.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go home, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.39,0:17:29.31,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.57,0:17:32.82,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But it isn’t impossible....
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.39,0:17:38.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Say, it’s best if we investigate these four snapping turtles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.19,0:17:40.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What would we be looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.53,0:17:52.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.21,0:17:57.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can’t let me raise them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.97,0:18:00.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we need to deal with all the paperwork first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.87,0:18:02.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So please give us about a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.96,0:18:04.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That’s so long...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:11.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I really have to wait an entire week?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.97,0:18:12.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.82,0:18:16.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we’ve got him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.82,0:18:20.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.90,0:18:22.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it was 304, 304...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.85,0:18:24.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:28.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.32,0:18:30.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It won’t work no matter how many times you try.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:34.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted to pay a one-week rental fee, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.54,0:18:40.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you leave it there for more than three days,\Nmanagement will confiscate the contents inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.15,0:18:42.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, actually, I just wanted to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.76,0:18:49.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, the coin locker was made\Nso that you can’t open it without a key.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:52.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.07,0:18:54.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind if we open the locker?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.54,0:18:55.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Police?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:13.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nihonmatsu-{\i1}san{\i0}, what’s the meaning behind this money?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.36,0:19:15.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:18.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you were in debt to someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.50,0:19:23.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you stole 3 million yen from\NFukurokoji-{\i1}san{\i0} last night, didn’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.77,0:19:27.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But once you put the money in\Nthe coin locker, you failed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.22,0:19:31.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was in luck, until...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:34.27,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I’m exhausted...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:36.92,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Hey now, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.92,0:19:38.40,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Let’s find a place to rest before we continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.40,0:19:40.94,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Damn, I’m screwed if they see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.94,0:19:41.76,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.28,0:19:45.91,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.15,0:19:53.29,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}This is bad, I have to hide this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:56.29,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oh, Minami-{\i1}chan{\i0}, Megumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.29,0:19:59.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But I was out of 100 yen coins...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.80,0:20:03.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So that’s why you ran to the park. To burn the evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.56,0:20:06.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You’d only need to retrieve the money once dawn broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.42,0:20:08.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a foolproof plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:11.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, something happened then that\Nyou couldn’t have possibly imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:24.16,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.16,0:20:25.66,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Why is this happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.32,0:20:27.45,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Hey, spit it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:29.45,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Give me back the key!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.54,0:20:39.63,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.17,0:20:42.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That’s what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:45.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your precious key ended up being swallowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.59,0:20:48.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought that something like that could happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.64,0:20:51.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But these are the results of our X-ray tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.35,0:21:00.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So you decided to report this to City Hall\Nso they’d let you capture the turtle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.86,0:21:05.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, you could have decided not to bother with that,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.89,0:21:08.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and just reported the loss of your locker key\Nto the company that deals with it, couldn’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.98,0:21:10.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn’t work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:16.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he had done that, they’d check to make sure the stuff\Nin his locker belonged to him after helping him open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.36,0:21:21.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If they found out about the 3 million yen inside,\Nthey’d be able to link it to the robbery from last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.96,0:21:23.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.32,0:21:26.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So he was left with no choice other than\Nto capture all the snapping turtles.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.87,0:21:28.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.47,0:21:30.85,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}You won’t get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.33,0:21:37.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.78,0:21:49.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, why are you letting them go like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.81,0:21:52.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Letting dangerous animals roam\Nin a park that belongs to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.60,0:21:54.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.10,0:21:57.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you’re in no position to criticize them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.79,0:22:02.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re under arrest for breaking and\Nentering, and the theft of 3 million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.84,0:23:33.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that’s good, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.38,0:23:35.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All four turtles have new owners now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.55,0:23:40.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he’s still pretty scary, but it’d\Nbe pretty cruel to abandon him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.01,0:23:41.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.53,0:23:43.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Something happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.11,0:23:46.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I heard a crane was spotted up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.17,0:23:47.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And, there’s more than one!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.94,0:23:48.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.58,0:23:51.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! We’re going to be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.03,0:23:55.77,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}After a turtle comes a crane.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.56,0:23:57.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That’s just great.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.13,0:24:04.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaitō Kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.79,0:24:06.96,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Five riot officers just under the window...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.56,0:24:09.96,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It looks hard to enter from here.{uso}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.57,0:24:11.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A blackout!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.00,0:24:14.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, the painting’s gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.27,0:24:18.51,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Right, it disappeared as if it were an illusion...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.81,0:24:23.98,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I’m going to rip your mask off once more, Kaitō Kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.98,0:24:29.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.28,0:24:35.03,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan’s Hint:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.28,0:24:35.03,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Illustration on an advance notice
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.40,0:24:38.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}A certain snobby Kid might show up\Nfor the new school term in April.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.33,0:24:39.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}What a kidder...
